title: Gold/Plat Mid + Jungle duo Looking for team
body:
Hi guys,

Title says it all really, we are two players from WA looking for a 5's team to play seriously. Both are in our 20's and prefer a 17+ team.
Watch the pro scene heavily and can aid with coaching/drafting/shotcalling.

If you're interested and want to chat let add me to chat
IGN: Avenuee
